excerpt.rendered:
A Set Of 2 Beautifully Handcrafted Terracotta Vases Hand, In A Versatile Urn & Dholak Shape, Handpainted With A Patch Of Beautiful Madhubani Art & Warli Art. The Urn Shaped Vase Is Handpainted In A Lovely Black With A Spiral Strip Of Madhubani Art Encompassing A Patch Of Gold Madhubani Figure In Contrasting Colours Of White Gold And Black.

The Dholak Shaped Vase Handpainted In A Lovely Gold With Patches Of Madhubani Art In Contrasting Colours Of Black And Gold.
